('content_read_tracking', 'Chris Graham', '', '11', 'Architecture', '', 'Licensed on the same terms as Composr', 'General-purpose has-read tracking. New [tt]MARK_READ[/tt] and [tt]HAS_READ[/tt] symbols allow you to track whether members have read any kind of content. Just place them in the appropriate templates. For example, [tt]{+START,IF,{$NOT,{$HAS_READ,news,{ID}}}}This is unread{+END}[/tt] in [tt]NEWS_BOX.tpl[/tt] and [tt]{$MARK_READ,news,{ID}}[/tt] in [tt]NEWS_ENTRY_SCREEN.tpl[/tt].', '11', '11.9', 1734984012),
